    </p>

    <!-- System B -->
    <p workspace="2.5in">
      System B:
      <m>\begin{aligned}
        x_1 - 2x_2 \amp= -1 \\
        -x_1 + 2x_2 \amp= 3
      \end{aligned}</m>
      Classification: ____________
      <br/>Sketch axes and both lines; explain your reasoning.
    </p>

    <!-- System C -->
    <p workspace="2.5in">
